# No additional GPIO constraints for COTS Microzed
# Microzed does not have on-board LEDs or buttons
# All GPIO pins are available through the expansion headers (JX1, JX2, JX3)
# Users can connect external LEDs/buttons to these expansion pins as needed
# Pin assignments should be added here based on specific external hardware connections
